Package: ROHMO
Title: Runs of Homozygosity and Mosaicism Detector
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Alejandro", "Cáceres", , "alejandro.caceres@isglobal.org", c("aut", "cre")),
	person("Laura", "Balagué-Dobón", ,"laura.balague@isglobal.org", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Laura Balagué-Dobón <laura.balague@isglobal.org>
Description: ROHMO is a tool to detect Runs of Homozygosity and Mosaic Chromosome Alterations from SNP array data. Also to plot the results along with the metrics evaluated for the detection.
